data.description: A  great 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath split level with great "bones" on a large lot  in Oreland PA.  2 car garage with a huge driveway with parking for many cars.  Updated heating and air, and hot water heater.  Stone Fireplace in the Family Room, and a built in bar.  Cathedral ceilings in the Living Room.  Crawl space.  Rear storage shed.  In Ground pool in "as is" condition, (may be a fill in).  Covered rear patio.    The house needs updating. and is being sold in "as is" condition.   (1008 Summit (updated renovated property) sold in August 2023 for $600k, similar size/style).
